@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Load offset 8.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Returns 0 on null input.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "operation_parameters" takes op as Integer returns Integer:
